hadiths[64]{hadithnumber,text}:
1322,"Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ney ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey kaha : jaao (qazi bin kar) logon key darmiyan faisley karo, unhoney kaha : Ameerul-momineen ! kya aap mujhey maaf rakhen gey, Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : ''tum isey kyon bura samajhtey ho, tumharey baap to faisley kiya kartey they? ''is par unhoney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna hai : ''jo qazi huwa aur usney adl insaf key sath faisley kiye to laaiq hai ke wo is sey barabar-sarabar chhoot jaaey.'' (yani na sawab ka mustahiq ho na azaab ka), iskey baad mein (bhalai ki) kya ummid rakhun, hadees main eik qissa bhi hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees gharib hai, merey nazdik iski sanad muttasil nahin hai. aur Abdul-Malik jis sey Moa'tamir ney isey riwayat kiya hai Abdul-Malik bin Abi Jameela hain. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai."
1323,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo qaza (Judje ya Haakim) ka mutalba karta hai wo apni zaat key hawaley kar diya jata hai (Allah ki madad uskey shamile haal nahin hoti) aur jis ko jabran qazi banaya jata hai, Allah uskey paas eik farishta bhejta hai jo usey raahe-raast par rakhta hai.''"
1324,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo qaza (haakim) ka Talib hota hai aur uskey liye sifarishi dhoondta hai, wo apni zaat key supurd kar diya jata hai, aur jis ko jabran qazi banaya gaya hai, Allah uskey paas eik farishta bhejta hai jo us ko raahe-raast par rakhta hai. '' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- aur ye Israel ki (sabiqa) riwayat sey jisey unhoney Abdul-A'alaa sey riwayat ki hai ziyada sahih hai."
1325,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jis shakhs ko mansab qaza (qaazi ke pad) par faaiz kiya gaya ya jo logon ka qazi banaya gaya, (goya) wo baghair chhuri key zibeh kiya gaya.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is tareeq sey Hasan gharib hai. 2- aur ye is sanad key ilawa dusri sanad sey bhi Abu-Hurera sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai inhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai."
1326,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab Haakim (Qazi) khub soch samajh kar faisla karey aur sahih baat tak pahunch jaey to uskey liye dohra ajr hai padhi. aur jab faisla karey aur ghalat ho jaey to (bhi) uskey liye eik ajr hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Amr bin al-Aas aur Aqba bin Aamir sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 2- Abu-Hurera ki hadees is tareeq sey Hasan gharib hai. hum isey basanad :(سفيان الثوري an يحيى بن سعيد الأنصاري) hadees mein (عبدالرزاق an معمر an سفيان الثوري) riwayat ki hai.
1327,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Muaz ko (Qazi bana kar) Yamen bheja , to aap ney puchha : ''tum kaisey faisla karogey? ''  unhoney kaha : main Allah ki kitab sey faisley karunga, aap ney farmaya : ''agar (us ka hukm) Allah ki kitab (Quran) mein mojud na ho to?'' Muaz ney kaha : to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki sunnat sey faisley karunga , aap ney farmaya : ''agar Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki sunnat mein bhi (us ka hukm) mojud na ho to? ''  Muaz ney kaha : (tab) main apni raey sey ijtihaad karunga. aap ney farmaya : ''Allah ka shukar hai jisney Allah key Rasool key qaasid ko (sawaab ki) tofiq bakhshi.''"
1328,Muaz sey isi tarah ki hadees marfooan marvi (riwayat hui) hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ko hum sirf isi tareeq sey jantey hain. 2- aur iski sanad merey nazdik muttasil nahin hai. 3- abu Aun Saqafi ka naam Muhammad bin Ubedullah hai.
1329,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''qiyamat key din Allah key nazdik sab sey ziyada mehbub aur bethney mein uskey sab sey qarib aadil hukmaran hoga, aur Allah key nazdik sab sey ziyada naa-pasandida aur us sey sab sey door bethney wala zalim hukmaran hoga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi tareeq sey jantey hain. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin abi Aufi (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1330,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah Qazi key sath hota hai padhi. jab tak wo zulm nahin karta , aur jab wo zulm karta hai to wo usey chhod kar alag ho jata hai. aur us sey shetan chimat jata hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum is ko sirf Imran bin Qataan ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
1331,Mujhse Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab tumharey paas do aadmi faisle key liye ayen to tum pehley key haq mein faisla na karo jab tak ke doosrey ki baat na sun lo padhi. anqarib tum jaan loge ke tum kaisey faisla karo.'' Ali (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : iskey baad main barabar faisley karta raha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai.
1332,"Unhoney Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna hai : ''jo bhi haakim hajat mandon , mohtajon aur miskinon key liye apney darwazey band rakhta hai to Allah Taala bhi uski zarurat , hajat aur maskanat key liye apney darwazey band rakhta hai.''  jab Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ney ye suna to logon ki zarurat key liye eik aadmi muqarrar kar diya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Amr bin Murra (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees gharib hai. 2- ye hadees doosrey tareeq sey bhi marvi hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 4- Amr bin Murra Juhni ki kunniyat abu-Maryam hai."
1333,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey Isi hadees ki tarah isi mafhoom ki hadees riwayat ki hai. Yazeed bin abi Maryam Sham key rehney waley hain aur Bareed bin abi Maryam Koofa key rehney waley hain aur abu-Maryam ka naam Amr bin Murra Juhni hai.
1334,"merey baap ney Ubedullah bin abi Bakra ko jo qazi they khat likha ke tum ghusse ki haalat mein fareeqain key barey mein faisley na karo, kyonkey mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna hai : ''haakim ghusse ki haalat mein fareeqain key darmiyan faisley na karey.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- abu-Bakra ka naam Nufai hai."
1335,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujhey (Qazi bana kar) Yamen bheja , jab main rawana huwa to aap ney merey peechhey (mujhey bulaney key liye) eik aadmi ko bheja , main aap key paas wapis aaya to aap ney farmaya : ''kya tum jantey ho ke mainey tumhen bulaney key liye aadmi kyon bheja hai? (ye kehney key liye ke) tum meri ijazat key baghair koi chiz na lena , isliye ke wo khayanat hai, aur jo shakhs khayanat karega qiyamat key din khayanat key maal key sath hazir hoga, yehi bataaney key liye mainey tumhen bulaya tha, ab tum apney kaam par jaao.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees gharib hai. 2- hum isey is tareeq sey ba-riwayat abu-Usaama jantey hain jisey unhoney Dawud Awadi sey riwayat ki hai. 3- is bab mein Adi bin Umaira , Barida , Mastur bin Shaddad , abu-Humed aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1336,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney faisley mein rishwat deney waley aur rishwat leney waley dono par lanat bheji hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye hadees abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman sey bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai unhen Abdullah bin Amr sey aur unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai. 3- aur abu-Salma sey unkey baap key wastey sey bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai lekin ye sahih nahin hai. 4- mainey Abdullah bin Abdur-Rehman Darmi ko kehtey suna ke abu-Salma ( abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman ( ki hadees jisey unhoney Abdullah bin Amr sey aur unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai is baab mein sab sey ziyada achvhhi aur sab sey ziyada sahih hai) jo aagey aa rahi hai ). 5- is bab mein Abdullah bin Amr , Aaisha , ibne Hadida aur Umme-Salma (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1337,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney rishwat deney waley aur rishwat leney waley dono par lanat bheji hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1338,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''agar mujhey khur bhi hadiya ki jaey to main qubul karunga aur agar mujhey uski dawat di jaey to main qubul karunga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Anas ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Ali , Aaisha , Mughira bin Shoba , Salman , Muawiya bin Haida aur Abdur-Rehman bin Alqama (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1339,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum log apna muqadma ley kar merey paas aatey ho main eik insan hi hun, ho sakta hai ke tum mein sey koi aadmi apna daawey bayan karney mein doosrey sey ziyada charb zabaan ho padhi. to agar main kisi ko uskey musalman bhai ka koi haq dilwa dun to goya main usey jahannam ka eik tukda kaat kar dey raha hun, lihaza wo is mein sey kuchh bhi na ley.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Umme-Salma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera aur Aaisha sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1340,"Do aadmi eik Hazare-maut sey aur eik Kanda sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaye. Hizrami ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! is (Kandi ( ney meri zamin par qabza kar liya hai, is par Kandi ney kaha : ye meri zamin hai aur merey qabze mein hai, is par is (Hizrami) ka koi haq nahin hai. Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Hizrami sey puchha : '' tumharey paas koi gawah hai?''  usney arz kiya : nahin, aap ney farmaya : ''phir to tum us sey qism hi ley saktey ho.'' , us aadmi ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! wo faajir (badkaar) aadmi hai usey iski parwah nahin ke wo kis baat par qism kha raha hai. aur na wo kisi chiz sey ehtiyat barat'ta hai, aap ney farmaya : ''us sey tum qism hi ley saktey ho.'' aadmi qism khaney chala to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney jab wo peeth pher kar janey laga farmaya : agar is ney zulm ke saath tumhara maal khaney key liye qism khai hai to wo Allah Taala sey us haal mein milega ke Allah us sey rukh pherey hoga. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Wayl bin Hajar ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein umr , ibne-Abbas , Abdullah bin Amr , aur Ash-as bin Qais (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1341,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apney khutbe mein farmaya : ''gawah muddai key zimme hai aur qism muddai aleh key zimme hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is hadees ki sanad mein kalam hai. Muhammad bin Ubedullah Arzami apney hifz key talluq sey hadees mein zaeef gardaney jatey hain. ibne-Mubarak waghera ney in ko zaeef thehraaya hai.
1342,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney faisla kiya ke qism muddai aleh par hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai ke gawah muddai key zimme hai aur qism muddai aleh par hai.
1343,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik gawah key sath muddai ki qism sey (muddai key haq mein) faisla diya. Rabeea kehtey hain : mujhey Saad bin Ubada key betey ney khabar di ke hamney Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ki kitab mein likha paya ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney ''eik gawah aur muddai ki qism sey (muddai key haq mein) faisla diya.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Ali , Jabir , ibne-Abbas aur Suraq (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 2- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees ke ''nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik gawah aur muddai ki qism sey (muddai key haq mein) faisla kiy '' Hasan gharib hai."
1344,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik gawah aur muddai ki qism sey (muddai key haq mein) faisla diya.
1345,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik gawah key sath muddai ki qism sey (muddai key haq mein) faisla kiya, Raavi kehtey hain : aur Ali ney bhi isi sey tumharey darmiyan faisla kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees ziyada sahih hai. 2- isi tarah Sufiyan Sory ney bhi ba-tareeq : (an Jaafar bin Muhammad an Abeeh an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) mursalan riwayat ki hai. aur Abdul-Azeez bin abu-Salma aur Yahya bin Saleem ney is hadees ko ba-tareeq : (an Jaafar bin Muhammad an Abeeh an Ali an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) (marfooan) riwayat kiya hai. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, un logon ki raey hai ke huquq aur amwaal key silsiley main eik gawah key sath muddai ko qism khilana jayez hai. Malik bin Anas , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi yehi qol hai. ye log kehtey hain ke eik gawah key sath muddai ki qism sey sirf huquq aur amwaal key silsiley hi mein faisla kiya jaeyga. 4- aur ehle-koofa waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm eik gawah key sath muddai ki qism sey faisla karney ko jayez nahin samajhtey."
1346,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney kisi mushtaraka (saajha) ghulam mein sey apna hissea azaad kiya.'' , aur uskey paas itna maal ho jo ghulam ki waajibi qeemat ko pahunch raha ho to wo us maal sey baqi sharikon ka hissa ada karega aur ghulam (pura) azad ho jaeyga warna jitna azad huwa hai utna hi azad hoga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- isey Salim bin Abdullah ney bhi ba-tareeq : (an Abeeh an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) isi tarah riwayat kiya hai."
1347,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney mushtaraka (saajha) ghulam mein sey apna hissa azad kiya aur uskey paas itna maal ho jo uski qeemat ko pahunch raha ho (to wo baqi sharikon ka hissa bhi ada karega) aur wo iskey maal sey azad ho jaeyga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1348,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney mushtaraka (saajha) ghulam mein sey apna hissa azad kiya to baqi hissey ki azadi bhi usi key maal sey hogi agar uskey paas maal hai, aur agar uskey paas maal nahin hai to us ghulam ki waajibi qeemat lagai jaeygi, phir ghulam ko pareshani mein daley baghair usey moqey diya jaeyga ke wo kamai kar key us shakhs ka hissa ada kar dey jisney apna hissa azad nahin kiya hai.'' Muhammad bin Bashaar sey bhi aisi hi riwayat hai aur is mein « شقصاً » key bajaey « شقیصا ». Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- aur isi tarah Aban bin Yazeed ney Qatada sey Saeed bin Abi Aruba ki hadees key jaisi riwayat ki hai. 3- aur Shoba ney bhi is hadees ko Qatada sey riwayat kiya hai aur is mein unhoney us sey azadi key liye kamai karaney ka zikr nahin kiya hai. 4- siaaya (kamai karaney) key silsiley mein ehle-ilm ka ikhtilaf hai, baaz ehle-ilm ney is barey mein siaaya ko jayez kaha hai. aur yehi Sufiyan Sory aur ehle-koofa ka bhi qol hai, aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi isi key qaail hain. 5- is bab mein Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai, 6- aur baaz ehle-ilm ney kaha hai ke jab ghulam do aadmiyon mein mushtaraka ho aur un mein sey eik apna hissa azad kar dey to agar uskey paas maal ho to wo apney saajhidaar key hissey ka tawaan (jurmaana) ada karega aur ghulam usi key maal sey azad ho jaeyga, aur agar uskey paas maal nahin hai to ghulam ko jitna azad kya gaya hai utna azad hoga, aur baqi hissey ki azadi key liye us sey kamai nahin karaai jaeygi. aur un logon ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi (riwayat hui) ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees ki taraf sey ye baat kahi hai, aur yehi ehale Madina ka bhi qol hai. aur Malik bin Anas , Shafai aur Ahmed bhi isi key qaail hain."
1349,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''umraa (umr bhar ke liye koi cheez ya hadiya) jis ko diya gaya uskey ghar walon ka ho jata hai.''  ya farmaya : ''umraa jis ko diya gaya uskey ghar walon ki meeras hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is baab mein Zaid bin Sabit , Jabir , Abu-Hurera , Aaisha , Abdullah bin Zuber aur Muawiya (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1350,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jis aadmi ko umraa (umr bhar ke liye koi cheez ya hadiya) diya gaya wo uska hai aur uskey ghar walon yani waarison ka hai kyonkey wo usi ka ho jata hai jis ko diya jata hai, umra deney waley ki taraf nahin laut'taa hai isliye ke usney aisa Atiya diya hai jis mein meeras sabit ho gaee hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- aur isi tarah Maamar aur deegar kaee logon ney Zohri sey Malik ki riwayat hi ki tarah riwayat ki hai aur baaz ney Zohri sey riwayat ki hai, magar usney is mein « ولعقبه » ka zikr nahin kiya hai. 3- aur ye hadees iskey ilawa aur bhi sanadon sey Jabir sey marvi hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''umraa jis ko diya jata hai uskey ghar walon ka ho jata hai.'' aur is mein « لعقبه » ka zikr nahin hai. ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 4- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, ye log kehtey hain ke jab deney wala ye kahey ke ye teri umr tak tera hai aur terey baad teri aulad ka hai to ye usi ka hoga jis ko diya gaya hai. aur deney waley key paas lot kar nahin jaeyga aur jab wo ye na kahey ke (teri aulad) ka bhi hai to jisey diya gaya hai uskey marney key baad deney waley ka ho jaeyga. Malik bin Anas aur Shafai ka yehi qol hai. 5- aur deegar kaee sanadon sey marvi hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''umraa (umr bhar ke liye koi cheez ya hadiya) jisey diya gaya hai uskey ghar walon ka ho jaeyga.''  6- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. wo kehtey hain : jis ko ghar diya gaya hai uskey marney key baad wo ghar uskey warison ka ho jaeyga agar-che uskey warison ko na diya gaya ho. Sufiyan Sory , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka yehi qol hai."
1351,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''umraa (umr bhar ke liye koi cheez ya hadiya) jis ko diya gaya uskey ghar walon ka hai aur raqbaa bhi jis ko diya gaya hai uskey ghar walon ka hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- aur baaz ney isi sanad sey abu-Zubair sey riwayat ki hai ke unhoney isey Jabir sey moqufan naqal kiya hai, isey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam tak marfoo nahin kiya hai. 3- Ruqbaa ki tafseer ye hai ke koi aadmi kahey ke ye chiz jab tak tum zinda rahogey tumhari hai aur agar tum mujh sey pehley mar gaey to ye phir meri taraf lot aayegi. 4- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai ke umra ki tarah ruqbaa bhi jisey diya gaya hai uskey ghar walon hi ka hoga. Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka yehi qol hai. aur ehle-koofa waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ney umra aur ruqbaa key darmiyan farq kiya hai, un logon ney umra ko to Maamar (jis key naam chiz di gaee thi) ki maut key baad uskey waarison ka haq bataya hai aur ruqba ko kaha hai ke waarison ka haq nahin hoga balke wo deney wali ki taraf lot jaeyga."
1352,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''suleh musalman key darmiyan nafiz (laagu) hogi siwaye aisi suleh key jo kisi halal ko haram kar dey ya kisi haram ko halal. aur musalman apni sharton key paband hain. siwaye aisi shart key jo kisi halal ko haram kar dey ya kisi haram ko halal.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1353,"Mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : ''jab tum mein sey kisi ka padosi uski deewar mein lakdi gaadney ki us sey ijazat talab karey to wo usey na rokey.'' Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney jab ye hadees bayan ki to logon ney apney sar jhuka liye to unhoney kaha : kya baat hai, main dekh raha hun ke tum log is sey aeraz kar (bach) rahey ho? Allah ki qism main isey tumharey shaanon (kandhon) par maar kar hi rahunga yani tum sey isey bayan kar key hi rahunga. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas aur Majmaa bin Jaariya (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. Shafai bhi isi key qaail hain. 4- baaz ehle-ilm sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai : jin mein Malik bin Anas bhi shamil hain ke uskey liye durust hai ke apney padosi ko deewar mein lakdi gaadney sey mana kar dey, pehla qol ziyada sahih hai."
1354,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''qasam usi chiz par waqey hogi jis par tumhara sathi (mukhalif paksh) qism ley raha hai (tauriya ka aetbar nahin hoga).'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- hum isey Hasheem hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain jisey unhoney Abdullah bin Abi Saleh sey riwayat ki hai. aur Abdullah bin Abi Saleh , Suhel bin abi Saleh key bhai hain. 3- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi isi key qaail hain. 4- Ibrahim Nakhai kehtey hain ke jab qism leney wala zalim ho to qism khaney waley ki niyat ka aetbar hoga, aur jab qism leney wala mazloom ho to qism leney waley ki niyat ka aetbar hoga."
1355,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''raasta saat haath (chaudaa) rakho.''
1356,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab raastey key silsiley main tum mein ikhtilaf ho to usey saat haath (chaudaa) rakho.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye (pichhli) Wakee ki hadees sey ziyada sahih hai. 2- Bashir bin Kaab ki hadees jisey unhoney Abu-Hurera sey riwayat ki hai Hasan sahih hai, aur baaz ney isey Qatada sey aur Qatada ney Bashir bin Nuhaiq sey aur Bashir ney Abu-Hurera sey riwayat ki hai aur ye ghair mehfooz hai, 3- is bab mein ibne-Abbas sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1357,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik bachchey ko ikhtiyar diya ke chahey wo apney baap key sath rahey aur chahey apni maa key sath. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Amr aur Abdul-Hameed bin Jaafar key dada (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka isi hadees par amal hai, ye log kehtey hain ke jab maa baap key darmiyan bachchey key silsiley mein ikhtilaf ho jaey to bachchey ko ikhtiyar diya jaeyga chahey wo apney baap key sath rahey aur chahey wo apni maa key sath rahey. yehi Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai. unka kehna hai ke jab bachcha kam-sin ho to uski maa ziyada mustahiq hai. aur jab wo saat saal ka ho jaey to us ko ikhtiyar diya jaey, chahey to baap key sath rahey ya chahey to maa key sath rahey."
1358,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''sab sey pakizah chiz jis ko tum khatey ho tumhari apni kamai hai aur tumhari aulad bhi tumhari kamai mein sey hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- baaz logon ney Imaara bin Umer sey aur Imaara ney apni maa sey aur un ki maa ney Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey riwayat ki hai, lekin aksar raawiyon ney « an أمّه » key bajaey « an عمته » kaha hai yani Imaara bin Umer ney apni phuphi sey aur unhoney Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey riwayat ki hai. 3- is bab mein Jabir aur Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain. 4- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. wo kehtey hain ke baap ko betey key maal mein kulli ikhtiyar hai wo jitna chahey ley sakta hai. 5- aur baaz kehtey hain ke baap apney betey key maal sey ba-waqt zarurat hi ley sakta hai."
1359,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki kisi biwi ney aap key paas piyaley mein khaney ki koi chiz hadiya ki, Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ney (ghussey mein) apney haath sey piyaley ko maar kar uskey andar ki chiz gira di, to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''khaney key badley khana aur piyaley key badley piyala hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1360,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik piyala udhaar liya wo toot gaya, to aap ney jin sey piyala liya tha unhen uska tawaan (jurmaana) ada kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees mehfooz nahin hai. 2- Suwed ney mujh sey wohi hadees bayan karni chahi thi jisey Sory ney riwayat ki hai. 3- Sory ki hadees ziyada sahih hai."
1361,"mujhey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key samney eik lashkar mein pesh kiya gaya, us waqt meri umr chaudah saal ki thi to aap ney mujhey (lashkar mein) qubul nahin kiya, phir aainda saal mujhey aap key samney eik aur lashkar mein pesh kiya gaya aur us waqt meri umr pandarah saal ki thi to aap ney mujhey (lashkar mein) qubul kar liya. Nafey kehtey hain : mainey umr bin abdul-Azeez sey is hadees ko bayan kiya to unhoney kaha : baligh aur nabaligh key darmiyan yehi had hai. unhoney apney aamilon ko likha ke jo pandarah saal key ho jaeyn (maale ghanimat sey) in ko hissa diya jaey. dusri sanad sey umr ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah ki hadees riwayat ki hai aur is mein ye zikr nahin kiya ke) umr bin abdul-Azeez ney apney aamilon ko likha ke nabaligh aur baligh ki yehi had hai) albatta Sufiyan bin Uena ney apni hadees mein ye bayan kiya hai ke Nafey kehtey hain ke hamney is hadees ko umr bin Abdul-Azeez sey bayan kiya to unhoney kaha : bachcha aur muqaatil (jo jang mein shirkat ka ehal ho) key darmiyan yehi had hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, Sufiyan Sory , ibne-Mubarak , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi isi key qaail hain. ye log kehtey hain ke jab bachcha pandarah saal mukammal kar ley to uska hukm wohi hoga jo mardon ka hota hai aur agar pandarah saal sey pehley hi us ko ehtilaam (sawapandosh) aaney lagey to bhi uska hukm mardon jaisa hoga. Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain : bulooghat (jawani) ki teen alamaten hain : bachcha pandarah saal ka ho jaey, ya us ko ehtilaam aaney lagey , aur agar umr aur ehtilaam na malum ho sakey to jab uskey naaf key nichey key baal ug ayen to wo baligh hai."
1362,"Merey mamu abu-Barda bin Niyar (Raziallahu anhu) merey paas sey guzrey aur unkey haath main eik jhandaa tha, mainey puchha : aap kahan ka irada rakhtey hain? kaha : mujhey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik aisey shakhs key paas bheja hai jisney apney baap ki (doosri) biwi sey shaadi kar rakhi hai taake main uska sar ley kar aaun. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Bara ki hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- Muhammad bin Is-haq ney bhi is hadees ko Adi bin Sabit sey aur Adi ney Abdullah bin Yazeed sey aur Abdullah ney Bara (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat ki hai. 3- ye hadees Ash-as sey bhi marvi hai unhoney Adi sey aur Adi ney Yazeed bin Bara sey aur Yazeed ney Bara (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat ki hai. 4- neez (isi ke saath) ye Ash-as sey marvi hai unhoney Adi sey aur Adi ney Yazeed bin Baraa sey aur Yazeed ney apney mamu sey aur unkey mamu ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai, 5- is bab mein Qurra Muzni sey bhi riwayat hai."
1363,"Eik Ansari ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas Zuber sey Harra ki naaliyon key barey mein jis sey log apney khajoor key darkht seenchte they jhagda kiya, Ansari ney Zuber sey kaha : pani chhod do taake behta rahey , Zuber ney uski baat nahin maana , to dono ney Rasoolullah ki khidmat mein apna maamla pesh kiya. Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Zuber sey farmaya : ''zubair ! (tum apney khet ko) sairab kar lo, phir apney padoshi key liye pani chhod do.''  (ye sun kar) Ansari ghussa ho gaya aur kaha : Allah key Rasool ! (aisa faisla) is wajeh sey ke wo aap ki phuphi ka ladka hai? (ye suntey hi) Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key chehra ka rang badal gaya, aap ney farmaya : ''Zubair ! tum apney khet sairab kar lo, phir pani ko rokey rakho yahan tak ke wo mundeer tak pahunch jaey.''  Zuber kehtey hain : Allah ki qism , mera guman hai ke usi silsiley mein ye aayat nazil hui : ( فلا وربك لا يؤمنون حتى يحكموك فيما شجر بينهم) ''aap key rab ki qism , wo log momin nahin ho saktey jab tak ke apney jhagdon mein) aey Nabi ( wo aap ka hukm na maan lein (Nisaa : 45).'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Shuaib bin abi Hamza ney Zohri sey aur Zohri ney Urwa bin Zuber sey aur Urwa ney Zuber sey riwayat ki hai aur Shuaib ney is mein Abdullah bin Zuber key wastey ka zikr nahin kiya hai. aur Abdullah bin Wahab ney Isey pehli hadees ki tarah hi Les aur Yunus sey riwayat kiya hai aur un dono ney Zohri sey aur Zohri ney Urwa sey aur Urwa ney Abdullah bin Zuber sey riwayat ki hai."
1364,"Eik Ansari shakhs ney martey waqt apney chhe ghulamon ko azad kar diya jabkey uskey paas unkey ilawa koi aur maal na tha, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko ye khabar mili to aap ney us aadmi ko sakht baat kahi , phir un ghulamon ko bulaya aur do do kar key unkey teen hissey kiye , phir unkey darmiyan qura andazi ki aur jin (do ghulamon) key naam qura nikla in ko azad kar diya aur chaar ko ghulam hi rehney diya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- aur ye aur bhi sanadon sey Imran bin Husain sey marvi hai. 3- is bab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, 4- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. aur yehi Malik , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai. ye log ye aur is tarah key doosrey mawaqe par qura andazi ko durust kehtey hain. 5- aur ehle-koofa waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm qura andazi ko jayez nahin samajhtey , is moqey par log kehtey hain ke har ghulam sey eik tihai azad kiya jaeyga aur do tihai qeemat ki azadi key liye kamai karaee jaeygi."
1365,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi mohrim (aehraam wale) rishte-daar ka Malik ho jaey to wo (rishte-daar) azad ho jaeyga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ko hum sirf Hammad bin Salma hi ki riwayat sey musnadan (marfooan ( jantey hain. 2- aur baaz logon ney is hadees key kuchh hissey ko Qatada sey aur Qatada ney Hasan sey aur Hasan ney umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey (moqufan) riwayat kiya hai. is sanad sey Muhammad bin Bakr Barsaai ney bayan kiya unhoney Hammad bin Salma sey aur Hammad ney Qatada aur Aasim ahwal sey aur Qatada aur Aasim ney Hasan Basri sey aur Hasan ney Samura sey aur Samura ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai ke aap ney farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi mohrim qurbat daar ka Malik ho jaey to wo azad ho jaeyga.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Muhammad bin Bakr key ilawa hum kisi ko nahin jantey hain jisney Aasim Ahwal ka zikr kya ho aur unhon (Aasim) ney Hammad bin Salma sey riwayat ki ho. 2- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi hadees par amal hai. 3- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai ke aap ney farmaya : '' jo shakhs kisi mohrim qurbat daar ka Malik ho jaey to wo azad ho jaeyga.'' isey Zamra bin Rabeea ney Sory sey riwayat kiya hai, unhoney Abdullah bin Dinar sey , aur Abdullah ney ibne-Umar sey aur ibne-Umar ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey. is hadees ki riwayat mein logon ney Zamra ki mutaabiat (pairwi) nahin ki hai. muhaddeseen key nazdik ye hadees ghalat hai."
1366,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo shakhs doosrey ki zamin mein un ki ijazat key baghair fasal boey, us ko fasal sey kuchh nahin milega wo sirf kharch ley sakta hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- hum isey ba-riwayat Abu-Is'haq sirf Shareek bin Abdullah hi key tareeq sey jantey hain. 3- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi hadees par amal hai aur yehi Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai.  4- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey is hadees key barey mein puchha to unhoney kaha : ye hadees Hasan hai, unhoney kaha : main isey ba-riwayat Abu-Is'haq sirf Shareek hi key tareeq sey janta hun. 5- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain ke hum sey Maaqil bin Malik Basraa ney basanad : (عقبة بن الأصم an عطاء an رافع بن خديج an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) isi tarah riwayat ki hai."
1367,"un key baap (Bashir) ney apney eik betey ko eik ghulam diya, wo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki khidmat mein aaye taake aap ko is par gawah banaeyn, to aap ney un sey puchha : kya tum ney apney tamam ladkon ko aisa hi ghulam Atiya mein diya hai padhi. jaisa is ko diya hai? '' kaha : nahin, aap ney farmaya : ''to isey wapis ley lo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye aur bhi sanadon sey Noman bin Bashir Raziallahu anhuma sey marvi hai. 3- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. ye log aulad key darmiyan (Atiya deney mein) barabari ko malhooz rakhney ko mustahab samajhtey hain, yahan tak ke baaz logon ney to kaha hai ke bosa leney mein bhi apni aulad key darmiyan barabari barqarar rakhey. 4- aur baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain : bakhshish aur Atiya main apni aulad yani beta aur beti key darmiyan bhi barabari barqarar rakhey. yehi Sufiyan Sory ka qol hai. 5- aur baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain : aulad key darmiyan barabari yehi hai ke meeras ki tarah ladkey ko ladki key do gunaa diya jaey."
1368,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''ghar ka padoshi ghar (khareedney) ka ziyada haqdaar hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Samura ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- aur Esa bin Yunus ney Saeed bin Abi Aruba sey unhoney Qatada sey aur Qatada ney Anas sey aur Anas ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi key misl (jaisi) riwayat ki hai. neez (isi ke saath) Saeed bin Abi Aruba sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai unhoney Qatada sey unhoney Hasan Basri sey aur Hasan Basri ney Samura sey aur Samura ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai. 2- is bab mein Shareed , abu-Raafey aur Anas sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 4- aur ehle-ilm key nazdik sahih Hasan ki hadees hai jisey unhoney Samura sey riwayat ki hai. aur hum Qatada ki hadees ko jisey unhoney Anas sey riwayat ki hai, sirf Esa bin Yunus hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain aur Abdullah bin Abdur-Rehman Altaa'fi ki hadees jisey unhoney Amr bin Shareed sey aur Amr ney apney walid sey aur unkey walid ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai, is baab mein Hasan hadees hai. aur Ibrahim bin Maisraa ney Amr bin Shareed sey aur Amr ney abu-Raafey sey aur abu-Raafey ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey suna ke merey nazdik dono hadisein sahih hain."
1369,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''padosi apney padosi (saajhi) key shufaa ka ziyada haqdaar hai, jab dono ka raasta eik ho to uska intizar kiya jaeyga padhi. agar-che wo mojud na ho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. hum abdul-Malik bin Suleman (Alaihissalam) key ilawa kisi ko nahin jantey hain jisney is hadees ko Ata sey aur Ata ney Jabir sey riwayat ki ho. 2- Shoba ney Abdul-Malik bin Suleman (Alaihissalam) par isi hadees ki wajeh sey kalam kiya hai. muhaddeseen key nazdik Abdul-Malik bharosemand aur maamoon hain, Shoba key ilawa hum kisi ko nahin jantey hain jisney Abdul-Malik par kalam kiya ho, Shoba ney bhi sirf isi hadees ki wajeh sey kalam kiya hai. aur Wakee ney bhi ye hadees Shoba sey aur Shoba ney Abdul-Malik bin Abi Suleman (Alaihissalam) sey riwayat ki hai. aur ibne-Mubarak ney Sufiyan Sory sey riwayat ki hai ke unhoney kaha : abdul-Malik bin Sufiyan meezaan (tarazu) hain yani ilm mein. 3- ehle-ilm ka isi hadees par amal hai ke aadmi apney shufaa ka ziyada haqdaar hai agar-che wo ghaaieb hi kyon na ho, jab wo ( safar waghera) sey wapis aayega to us ko shufaa milega chaahe is par lambi muddat guzar chuki ho."
1370,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab had bandi ho jaey aur raastey alag alag kar diye jaeyn to shufaa nahin.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- isey baaz logon ney abu-Salma sey aur unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mursalan riwayat kiya hai. 3- Sahaba kiram mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka jin mein umr bin Khattab aur Usman bin Affaan bhi shamil hain isi par amal hai aur baaz Tabe-een fuqaha jaisey umr bin Abdul-Azeez waghera bhi isi key qaail hain. aur yehi ehale-Madina ka bhi qol hai, jin mein Yahya bin Saeed Ansari , Rabeea bin abu-Abdur-Rehman aur Malik bin Anas shamil hain, Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi isi key qaail hain, ye log sirf saajhi-daar key liye hi shufaa ke haq key qaail hain. aur jab padosi saajhi-daar na ho to uskey liye shufaa key haq  key qaail nahin. Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke padosi key liye bhi shufaa hai aur un logon ney marfoo hadees sey daleel di hai jis mein Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam farmatey hain : ''ghar ka padosi ghar ka ziyada haqdaar hai.''  neez farmatey hain : ''padosi apney sey lagi hui zamin ya makaan ka ziyada haqdaar hai aur yehi Sory , ibne-Mubarak aur ehle-koofa ka bhi qol hai."
1371,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''saajhi-daar ko shufaa ka haq hasil hai aur shufaa har chiz mein hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- hum is hadees ko is tarah (marfooan) sirf abu-Hamza Sukkri hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- is hadees ko kaee logon ney abdul-Azeez bin Rafeea' sey aur Abdul-Azeez ney ibne-Abi Muleka sey aur ibne-Abi Muleka ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mursalan riwayat kiya hai. aur yehi ziyada sahih hai. is sanad mein Hannaad ney abu-Bakar bin Ayash sey abu-Bakar bin Ayash ney Abdul-Azeez bin Rafeea' sey aur Abdul-Azeez ney ibne-Abi Muleka sey aur ibne-Abi Muleka ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah ki hadees riwayat ki hai, is mein ibne-Abbas ka wasta nahin hai. 3- aur isi tarah kaee aur logon ney Abdul-Azeez bin Rafeea' sey isi key jaisi hadees riwayat ki hai aur is mein bhi ibne-Abbas ka wasta nahin hai. 4- abu-Hamza (ye marfoo) ki hadees sey ziyada sahih hai. abu-Hamza bharosemand hain. mumkin hai ye khata abu-Hamza key ilawa kisi aur sey hui ho. is sanad mein Hannad ney Abul Ahwas sey aur Abul Ahwas ney Abdul-Azeez bin Rafeea' sey aur Abdul-Azeez ney ibne-Abi Muleka sey aur ibne-Abi Muleka ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey abu-Bakar bin Ayash ki hadees ki tarah riwayat ki hai. 5- aksar ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke shufaa ka haq sirf ghar aur zamin mein laagu hoga. un logon ki raey mein shufaa har chiz mein nahin. 6- aur baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain : shufaa har chiz mein hai. lekin pehla qol ziyada sahih hai."
1372,"Eik shakhs ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey luqtaa (giri padi chiz) key barey mein poochha, to aap ney farmaya : ''saal bhar tak iski pehchan karaao, phir is ka sar band, is ka bartan aur iski thaili pehchan lo, phir isey kharch kar lo aur agar is ka Malik aa jaey to isey ada kar do.''  us aadmi ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! gumshuda bakri ka kya hukm hai? aap ney farmaya : ''usey pakad kar baandh lo, kyonkey wo tumharey liye hai, ya tumharey bhai key liye, ya bhediye key liye.'' us aadmi ney arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! gumshuda oont ka kya hukm hai? is par Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam naraz ho gaey yahan tak ke aap key gaal lal peela ho gaey. ya aap ka chehra lal peela ho gaya aur aap ney farmaya : ''tum ko us sey kya sarokaar? uskey sath uska joota aur uski mushk hai padhi. (wo pani par ja sakta hai aur darkht sey kha sakta hai) yahan tak ke apney Malik sey ja miley.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Zaid bin Khalid ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- in sey aur bhi turq sey ye hadees marvi (riwayat hui) hai. Munbais key Mola Yazeed ki hadees jisey unhoney Zaid bin Khalid sey riwayat ki hai Hasan sahih hai. 3- aur un sey ye aur bhi kaee sanadon sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai."
1373,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey luqtaa ( giri padi chiz ( key barey mein puchha gaya to aap ney farmaya : ''saal bhar uski pehchan karaao padhi. , agar koi pehchan bata dey to usey dey do , warna uskey daat aur sarband ko pehchan lo , phir usey kha jaao . phir jab uska Malik aaye to usey ada kar do.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Zaid bin Khalid ki hadees is tareeq sey Hasan gharib hai. 2- Ahmed bin Hanbal kehtey hain : is baab mein sab sey ziyada sahih yehi hadees hai. 3- ye un sey aur bhi kaee sanadon sey marvi hai. 4- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. ye log luqtaa sey faeyda uthaney ko jayez samajhtey hain, jab eik saal tak uska aelan ho jaey aur koi pehchanney wala na miley. Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka yehi qol hai. 5- aur Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke wo eik saal tak luqtaa ka aelan karey agar uska Malik aa jaey to theek hai warna wo usey sadqa kar dey. Sufiyan Sory aur Abdullah bin Mubarak ka yehi qol hai. aur yehi ehle-koofa ka bhi qol hai. 6- luqtaa uthaney wala jab maaldaar ho to ye log luqtaa sey faeyda uthaney ko uskey liye jayez nahin samajhtey hain. 7- Shafai kehtey hain : wo is sey faeyda uthaey agar-che wo maaldaar ho, isliye ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key zamaney mein Ubai-bin Kaab ko eik thaili mili jis mein sau Dinar they to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unhen hukm diya ke wo uska aelan karen phir us sey faeyda uthaeyn, aur Ubai-bin Kaab Sahaba mein khushhal logon mein they aur bahut maaldaar they, phir bhi Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unhen pehchan karaney ka hukm diya aur jab koi pehchanney wala nahin mila to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unhen kha janey ka hukm diya. (doosri baat ye ke) agar luqta sirf unhin logon key liye jayez hota jin key liye sadqa jayez hai to Ali (Raziallahu anhu) key liye jayez na hota, isliye ke Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key zamane main eik Dinar mila , unhoney (saal bhar tak) uski pehchan karwaai lekin koi nahin mila jo usey pehchanta to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unhen kha janey ka hukm diya halanke unkey liye sadqa jayez nahin tha. 8- baaz ehle-ilm ney rukhsat (chhoot) di hai ke jab luqtaa maamuli ho to luqtaa uthaney wala is sey faeyda utha sakta hai aur is ki pehchan karwana zaruri nahin. 9- baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain : jab wo eik Dinar sey kam ho to wo uski eik hafta tak pehchan karwaaey. ye Is-haq bin Ibrahim bin Raahviya ka qol hai. 10- is bab mein Ubai-bin Kaab , Abdullah bin Amr , Jarood bin Muallaa , Ayaaz bin Himaar aur Jareer bin Abdullah sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1374,"Main Zaid bin Sohaan aur Salman bin Rabeea key sath nikla to mujhey (raastey mein) eik kodaa pada mila. ibne Numer ki riwayat mein hai ke mainey pada huwa eik kodaa paya. to mainey usey utha liya to un dono ney kaha : isey rehney do, (na uthaao) mainey kaha : main isey nahin chhod sakta ke isey darindey kha jaeyn , main isey zarur uthaaunga, aur is sey faeyda uthaaunga. phir main Ubai-bin Kaab key paas aaya , aur un sey iskey barey mein puchha aur un sey puri baat bayan ki to unhoney kaha : tum ney achchha kiya, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key zamane mein , mainey eik thaili pai jis mein sau Dinar they, usey ley kar mein aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaya , aap ney mujh sey farmaya : ''eik saal tak iski pehchan karaao.''  mainey eik saal tak uski pehchan karaai lekin mujhey koi nahin mila jo usey pehchanta , phir main usey ley kar aap key paas aaya. aap ney farmaya : ''eik saal tak aur iski pehchan karaao.'' mainey uski pehchan karaai, phir usey ley kar aap key paas aaya. to aap ney farmaya : ''eik saal tak aur iski pehchan karaao.''  aur farmaya : ''iski ginti kar lo, uski thaili aur uskey sarband ko khub achchhi tarah pehchan lo agar isey talash karney wala aaye aur iski tadaad, iski thailii aur iskey sarband key barey mein bataey to usey dey do warna tum isey apney kaam mein laao.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1375,"umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko khaibar mein (maale ghanimat sey) kuchh zamin mili , to unhoney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! khaibar mein mujhey maal mila hai is sey ziyada umda maal mujhey kabhi nahin mila. (iskey barey mein) aap mujhey kya hukm farmatey hain? aap ney farmaya : ''agar chaho to iski asal rok lo aur isey (pedawar ko) sadqa kar do, to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney isey is tarah sey sadqa kiya ke asal zamin na bechi jaey, na hiba ki jaey, aur na kisi ko virasat mein di jaey padhi. , aur isey faqiron mein , rishtedaaron mein , ghulam azad karney mein , Allah key raastey (jihad) mein , musafiron mein aur mehmano mein kharch kiya jaey. aur jo is ka wali (nigran) ho uskey liye is mein sey maroof tareeqey sey khaney aur dost ko khilaney mein koi harj nahin hai, jabkey wo is mein sey zakhira andozi karney wala na ho. ibn Aun kehtey hain : mainey isey Muhammad bin Sirin sey bayan kiya to unhoney (غير متمول فيه) key bajaey (غير متأثل مالا) kaha. ibne Aun kehtey hain : mujh sey isey eik aur aadmi ney bayan kiya hai ke usney us waqf namey ko padha tha jo eik lal chamdey par tehreer tha aur is mein bhi (غير متأثل مالا) key alfaz they. Ismail kehtey hain : mainey us waqf namey ko Ubedullah bin umr key betey key paas padha , is mein bhi (غير متأثل مالا) key alfaz they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. pahle ke logon mein sey hum kisi ko nahin jantey hain jisney zamin waghera ko waqf karney mein ikhtilaf kiya ho."
1376,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab insan mar jata hai to uskey amal ka silsila band ho jata hai siwaye teen chizon key : eik sadqae-jaariya padhi. hai, doosra aisa ilm hai padhi. jis sey log faeyda uthaeyn aur teesra nek aur Saleh aulad hai padhi. jo uskey liye dua karey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1377,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''bezaban (janwer) ka zakham rayegaan (bekar) hai, kunwen aur kaan mein gir kar koi mar jaey to wo bhi rayegaan hai padhi. , aur jahiliyat key dafeeney mein paanchwan hissa hai.'' Muallif ney apni sanad sey b-tareeq :(عن ابن شهاب an سعيد بن المسيب وأبي سلمة an أبي هريرة an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) isi tarah ki hadees riwayat ki hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Jabir Amr bin Auf Muzni aur Ubada bin Samit (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Malik bin Anas kehtey hain ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki hadees « العجماء جرحها جبار » (Wal Maadan Jabbar) ki tafseer ye hai ke chopayon sey lagey huye zakham rayegaan hain is mein koi diyat nahin hai. 4- « العجماء جرحها جبار » ki baaz ulama ney yehi tafseer ki hai, ye log kehtey hain ke bezaban janwer wo hain jo apney Malik key paas sey bidak kar bhag jaeyn , agar unkey bidak kar bhagney ki haalat mein kisi ko un sey zakham lagey ya chot aa jaey to janwer waley par koi tawaan (jurmana) nahin hoga. 5- « العجماء جرحها جبار » ki tafseer mein Malik kehtey hain : jab koi shakhs kaan khudwaaye aur is mein koi gir jaey to kaan khudwaney waley par koi tawaan (jurmana) nahin hai, isi tarah kunwen hai jab koi musafiron waghera key liye kunwaan khudwaaey aur is mein koi shakhs gir jaey to khudwaane waley par koi tawaan nahin hai. 6- « وفي الركاز الخمس » ki tafseer mein Malik kehtey hain : (rikaz) ehale jahiliyat ka dafeena hai agar kisi ko jahiliyat ka dafeena miley to wo paanchwan hissa sultan key paas (sarkari khazane mein) jama karega aur jo baqi bacheyga wo uska hoga."
1378,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney koi banjar zamin ( jo kisi ki milkiyat mein na ho ( abad ki to wo usi ki hai kisi zalim shakhs ki rag ka haq nahin ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- baaz logon ney isey Hisham bin Urwa sey unhoney apney walid Urwa sey aur Urwa ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mursalan riwayat ki hai, padhi. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka isi hadees par amal hai aur Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi yehi qol hai, ye log kehtey hain ke haakim ki ijazat key baghair ghair abad zamin ko abad karna jayez hai, 4- baaz ulama kehtey hain : haakim ki ijazat key baghair ghair abad zamin ko abad karna jayez nahin hai, lekin pehla qol ziyada sahih hai, 5- is bab mein Jabir , Kasir key dada Amr bin Auf Muzni aur Samra sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 6- hum sey abu-Musa Muhammad bin Musanna ney bayan kya, wo kehtey hain ke mainey abu-Waleed Tiyalisi sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key qol (ولیس لعرق ظالم حق) ka matlab puchha , unhoney kaha : « العرق الظالم » sey murad wo غاصب hai jo dusron ki chiz zabardasti ley . mainey kaha : is sey murad wo shakhs hai jo doosrey ki zamin mein darkht lagaey ? unhoney kaha : wohi shakhs murad hai."
1379,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo shakhs ghair abad zamin (jo kisi ki milkiyat mein na ho) abad karey to wo usi ki hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1380,"wo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaye aur aap sey jaagir mein namak ki kaan maangi to aap ney unhen dey di, lekin jab wo peeth pher kar wapis janey lagey to majlis mein mojud eik aadmi ney arz kya : jantey hain ke aap ney jaagir mein usey kya diya hai? aap ney isey jaagir mein aisa pani diya hai jo kabhi band nahin hota hai. (us sey barabar namak nikalta rahega) to aap ney us sey usey wapis ley liya , usney aap sey puchha : peelu key darakhton ki kon si jagah (bator thikana) gheri jaey ? aap ney farmaya : '' jis zamin tak oonton key paaon na pahunchey '' (jo aabadi aur charaagaah sey kafi door hon) . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abyaz ki hadees gharib hai, 2- mainey Quteba sey puchha kya aap sey Muhammad bin Yahya bin Qais Maaribi ney ye hadees bayan ki to unhoney iqrar kya aur kaha : haan."
1381,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unhen hazre-maut main eik zamin bator jageer di. aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ko bheja taake wo zamin unhen bator jageer dey den . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai.
1382,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo bhi musalman koi darkht lagata hai ya fasal bota hai aur is mein sey insan ya charind ya parind khata hai to wo uskey liye sadqa hota hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu-Ayyub , Jabir , Umme Mubashshir aur Zaid bin Khalid (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1383,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney khaibar walon key sath khaibar ki zamin sey jo bhi phal ya ghalla hasil hoga uskey aadhey par maamla kya padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Anas , ibne-Abbas , Zaid bin Sabit aur Jabir (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, padhi. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. ye log aadhey , tihai ya chothai ki shart par muzaar'at karney mein koi harj nahin samajhtey , 4- aur baaz ehle-ilm ney ye ikhtiyar kya hai ke beej zamin wala dega , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi yehi qol hai, 5- baaz ehle-ilm ney tihai ya chothai ki shart par muzaar'at ko makrooh samjha hai, lekin wo tihai ya chothai ki shart par khajoor key darakhton ki seenchai karaney mein koi harj nahin samajhtey hain. Malik bin Anas aur Shafai ka yehi qol hai, 6- baaz log mutlaqan muzaar'at ko durust nahin samajhtey albatta soney ya chaandi ( naqdi) key iwaz kiraaye par zamin leney ko durust samajhtey hain."
1384,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hamen eik aisey kaam sey mana farma diya jo hamarey liye mufeed tha, wo ye ke jab hum mein sey kisi key paas zamin hoti to wo us ko (kheti key liye) kuch pedawar ya rupyon key iwaz dey deta . aap ney farmaya : '' jab tum mein sey kisi key paas zamin ho to wo apney bhai ko) muft ( dedey. ya khud kheti karey padhi. ''."
1385,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney muzaar'at ko haram nahin kya, lekin aap ney eik doosrey key sath narmi karney ka hukm diya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Raafey ki hadees mein) jo ooper mazkur hui ( iztirab hai. kabhi ye hadees b-wasta Raafey bin khadij unkey chachaaon sey riwayat ki jati hai aur kabhi b-wasta Raafey bin khadeej Zuher bin Raafey sey riwayat ki jati hai, ye bhi unkey eik chacha hain, 3- aur un sey ye hadees mukhtalif tareeqey par riwayat ki gaee hai, 4- is bab mein Zaid bin Sabit aur Jabir Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
